      <p style="margin:24px 0 0; font-size:18px; line-height:1.7; color:#4A4A42;">Spend the day at the Sanctuary and help support rescued wild animals. 100% of event proceeds go to The Wild Animal Sanctuary.</p>
      <a href="#register" class="btn-pill" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:32px; font-size:16px; color:#FBF8F1; background:#2B3A2D; padding:17px 36px;">Register for a Class</a>
